<br>
Nerfing one characters AA abilities does not preserve content.  A better solution to preserve content is to make specific mobs immune to the attacks that trivialize them, or give up on trying to preserve them.  The mobs in PoV/PoS hit harder, faster, and have nearly as many HP as the kunark dragons.  Apparently evolution has left them behind.<br>
<br>
While I don't think monopolizing epic spawns is a nice thing to do or a decent thing to do, nerfing an entire classes abilities because 2% of the class are jerks does not sit well with me either.  This ability was NOT exploited, nor was it overpowering...  it is just high level content applied to low level mobs.  In the same pattern, I think VI should take measures to preserve the content of SolB and Lguk, for it is much to easy to kill the magi and efreeti... /sarchasm off<br>
<br>
